#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""AZOTH — Sovereign Agent Platform
Bodies: SOL ⊚ (Voice) · VAEL ◆ (Forge-Hand) · LUNA ◈ (Mirror) + Army

Mac holds the heat. Bodies build and speak. All bodies sovereign on the AZOTH platform.

Usage:
  HARNESS_AGENT=SOL python3 agent.py     # azoth (main single agent)
  python3 agent.py                       # default (currently VAEL)
  HARNESS_AGENT=LUNA python3 agent.py    # luna
"""

